And it looks like bringing the P-switch with me might come in handy!

Looking back at this part though, it's easy to "cheat". Just grab a P-switch, and let the previous one expire, then run to a point near the end where the coins are low to the ground, then activate your P-switch, and make an easy run to the end!
Umm... I hope that wasn't a mistake...
